'We have to bounce back against Dortmund after the international break. It will be an important game, and then the Champions League and the DFB Pokal return. 

'Those are the important games and we have to be in great shape.'

Bayern visit Borussia Dortmund on April 4 before a German Cup quarter-final away at Bayer Leverkusen four days later.

